    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction has been reviewed. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed and all show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors remain as documented epistemic gaps. The package is accepted as a complete and transparent record of the credibility shortfalls; the device submission decision remains Not Accepted pending remediation of identified gaps.",
